> [troopjs-contrib-browser](https://github.com/troopjs/troopjs-contrib-browser) module extends the core TroopJS DOM package
> with features for building single page application easier, notablely the `troopjs-contrib-browser/mvc/controller/widget`
> widget consolidates an MVC pattern by implementing an centralized application controller that consume URI changes and push
> application states (data) to be consumed by other widgets through hub events.
